org.jooby.assets

Class SvgSprites

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jooby.assets.AssetOptions
      • org.jooby.assets.AssetAggregator
        • org.jooby.assets.SvgSprites

  • public class SvgSprites
extends AssetAggregator

    svg-sprites

    An AssetAggregator that creates SVG sprites with PNG fallbacks at needed sizes via dr-svg-sprites.

    usage

     assets {
   fileset {
     sprite: svg-sprites
     home: home.scss
   }

   svg-sprites {
     spriteElementPath: "images/svg-source",
     spritePath: "css"
   }
 }

    The spriteElementPath contains all the *.svg files you want to process. The spritePath indicates where to save the sprite, here you will find the following generated files: css/sprite.css, css/sprite.svg and css/sprite.png.

    options

     assets {
   fileset {
     sprite: svg-sprites
     home: home.scss
   }

   svg-sprites {
     spriteElementPath: "images/svg-source",
     spritePath: "css",
     layout: "vertical",
     sizes: {
       large: 24,
       small: 16
     },
     refSize: "large"
   }
 }

    Please refer to dr-svg-sprites for more details.

    Author:
    edgar
